  "title": "A Comedy Show at the End of the World",
  "description": "Comedy may not have prevented the apocalypse, but it can make it a lot more fun! Gather around the barrel-fire with tolerated community member Johnny as he draws on his showbiz career from the Before Times to put on a night of post-apocalyptic sketch comedy guaranteed to make you say \"okay, I guess he still serves a function\"!",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Jon Blair<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Jon Blair<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Joel Bazin<br/>",
  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "A Comedy Show at the End of the World is about Johnny, a former comedy writer, who tries to put on a funny sketch show after the world ends. Using whatever props and costumes he can find or make from trash, he wants to make the survivors laugh and show that comedy still matters.",
